tive selection in Tbx3 was not found, which would suggest that the function of this gene has not been changed. Together, our findings support the hypothesis that the modulation of the spatiotemporal expression patterns of multiple functional conserved genes control limb morphology and drive morphological change in the diversification of mammalian limbs.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Dai, Mengyao", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wang, Yao", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fang, Lu", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Irwin, David M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhu, Tengteng", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhang, Junpeng", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhang, Shuyi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wang, Zhe", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schubert, Michael", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3f33c6ddfbe085a7478127f87dd2fa7b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/de08ba7b00e35a116c9dde9a72a03f2987690e461155f141adcd4136cd8e46c1", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/FRZ3SV36", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/FRZ3SV36", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/6269070b3969f1153d69b3a5f0321451!/b292010-294466", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"